description: 1.Please remover the blue film before use it. 2.Please don't try to clean the stamper with harsh chemicals such as nail polish remover. To reach the best results,clean it with a Lint Roller or sticky tape to remove excess polish and dust/fluff. 3.Notice: Due to different nail polish quality,some nail polish is not suitable for stamping,so please choose Biutee nail stamping polish or nail stamping polish gel.
